nokh der milkhome hot men genumen keyn DONBAS.

00:00:10.305 --> 00:00:15.115
m'hot u- un- DONBAS iz a shtot in Rusland vu m'hot zey ge- tsekna-

00:00:10.315 --> 00:00:12.375
vos iz, vos iz DONBA-

00:00:15.115 --> 00:00:16.755
di daytshe hobn zi tseklapt

00:00:16.755 --> 00:00:19.718
un m'hot zi gedarft oyfboyen, hot men genumen yidn

00:00:19.718 --> 00:00:21.566
mener, froyen, ki-

00:00:21.566 --> 00:00:26.972
un m'hot geshlept keyn DONBAS. s'iz geshtanen iberal a- DONBAS KLECHET. DONBAS ruft.

00:00:27.467 --> 00:00:31.725
