00:00:44.794 --> 00:00:47.360
iz er avekgegangen in der fri un iz aheymgekumen oyf der nakht.

00:00:47.464 --> 00:00:51.423
dos iz geven a groyse zakh, me zol im nisht shlepn keyn DONBAS.

00:00:52.510 --> 00:00:58.764
ikh hob a kind. ikh hob gehat a PASAPORT, vos i- a kind oykh fun dray yor, hot men mikh oykh nisht getshepet.

00:01:00.829 --> 00:01:02.880
